uxterm*font: -*-terminus-medium-*-*-*-12-*-*-*-*-*-iso8859-*

!*faceName: dejavu sans mono
!*faceSize: 8
!!!! end fonts !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!


